profile:
Standard Garage stands apart from the competitors with a friendly one on one service, affordable pricing, and attention to detail. Locally owned and operated in Windsor Ontario with 35 years of experience in the garage door repair and garage door opener industry.

Call or Text Today 519-999-1724 

Our business hours are Monday thru Friday from 8:00 to 5:00. 24-hour emergency service is available. Prompt and courteous service guaranteed.

profile:
Established since 1976, Dor-Co Garage Doors, is under the direction of local owner Jerry Cousineau.

Dor-Co's featured products include garage doors, door & gate operators, sectional doors, dock levelers, dock seals, rapid roll doors, automated doors, garage door openers, bug screens, keyless entry systems and more. We offer the best in garage door products from Garaga, C.H.I, Amarr, Blue Giant, Pentalift, Liftmaster, Besam, Albany International and more for Industrial, Commercial and Residential Applications

We offer Overhead Doors in Steel, Aluminum, Rolling Steel, Insulated and Non-Insulated, Truck Doors, Sliding Barn Door Hardware, Dock Levelers, Folding Room Dividers, PVC Strip Doors, Toilet Partitions and we repair truck doors as well.

 The people at Dor-Co Garage Doors will offer good advice for the do-it-yourselfer, to help make installing these products less of a chore. If you prefer, our trained staff can install it for you!
